The paper discusses the use of columnar databases for AI analytics, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also extensively discusses the use of AI algorithms, specifically Deep Learning and Machine Learning, for data analysis (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also discusses featurization techniques, which are commonly used in data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper proposes an integrated architecture for columnar databases and AI, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
